The paper discusses the use of reinforcement learning and AI in solving complex problems with high dimensional state spaces, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus of the paper is on improving safety in RL, which involves the use of robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also evaluates the approach using visual representations, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV).
